        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>
                    <emph type="bold">REVISION DESCRIPTION</emph>
                </para>
                <para>The start and end dates changed for the truck models.</para>
                <para>
                    <title>RECALL DESCRIPTION</title>
                </para>
                <para>The flex plate mounting bolts may bottom out in the torque converter housing resulting in poor
                    clamp load.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
